Kipketer becomes the first elite Kenyan athlete to be banned by AIU this year.
Lat year, AIU also banned 2017 World 1,500m champion Elijah Manang'oi for two years for a similar offence.
Former world marathon record holder Wilson Kipsang and 2017 London Marathon champion Daniel Wanjiru were also handed four-year bans for doping offences in 2020. Elijah Manang'oi is the 2017 World 1,500m champion. Manang'oi is the 2017 World 1,500m champion. Social media giant cites the risk of further violence following the assault on the US Capitol by his supporters During his four years in office, Trump used Twitter to ridicule his political opponents, labelling them with mocking nicknames. This comes after his repeated rejection of the election result and violent protests by his supporters.